{"tid":1330782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"古代兵器今用 [絆馬索]","createTime":"2019-07-18T16:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T18:47:09.000Z","uid":254838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"604b9f7e373c3788c645108b523509f0c4e99a3f","tid":1330782,"uid":254838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:45:49.000Z","msg":"古代用麻繩，現代可以用魚絲，既透明輕巧，又夠靱度。兩頭綁上重物方便投擲，由上而下擲可以制止手部活動能力，擲向腳部，行多步即時仆街。大量投擲可凍結敵方機動能力。"},{"pid":"500df8cb696b75188467c0af63e6a755f2d9c124","tid":1330782,"uid":254838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"604b9f7e373c3788c645108b523509f0c4e99a3f","tid":1330782,"uid":254838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:45:49.000Z","msg":"古代用麻繩，現代可以用魚絲，既透明輕巧，又夠靱度。兩頭綁上重物方便投擲，由上而下擲可以制止手部活動能力，擲向腳部，行多步即時仆街。大量投擲可凍結敵方機動能力。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:57:38.000Z","msg":"小弟不才，出親post都無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a770379c5c36f29539d60d667f6f0adcb8f4ba82","tid":1330782,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9bef6588977235947dee12f6e3a5a118cccfa8","tid":1330782,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"有無圖"},{"pid":"91667d783b8b9add3e4e4468a7382abcce247533","tid":1330782,"uid":254838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c9bef6588977235947dee12f6e3a5a118cccfa8","tid":1330782,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"有無圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:21:51.000Z","msg":"搵唔到圖，得條殘體link<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sohu.com/n/492599055/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sohu.com%2Fn%2F492599055%2F&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHEw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=63476908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.sohu.com/n/492599055/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上喺